app.controllers.admin.name: app.controllers.admin
app.controllers.admin.description: This is the admin controller. It provides methods for admin routing like in CakePHP. Urls containing /admin/ are directed here an then matched on their real target controllers.
example: /admin/methods/add is mapped onto /methods/admin_add on the server. To enabled admin routing
